quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,82,"(E kituufu kiri nti) abo abakkiriza ne batatabula kweyisa bubi (Shirik), mu bukkiriza bwabwe, abo nno be balina e mirembe era abo be baalungamizibwa"
  6,83,"Obwo bwe bujulizi bwaffe bwe twawa Ibrahim akozese ku bantube (e kyamussa mu kifo e kyenjawulo), bulijjo tusitula amadaala gw’oyo gwetuba twagadde, anti mazima ddala Mukama omulabiriziwo agoba nsonga mumanyi nnyo"
  6,84,"Era twamugabira (Ibrahim) Ishak ne Yakub, bombi twabalungamya nga n’okusooka twalungamya Nuhu, ne mu zadderye twalungamya Dauda ne Sulaiman ne Ayub ne Yusuf ne Musa ne Haruna, na bwekityo nno bwe tusasula abalongoofu"
  6,85,"Ne Zakariya ne Yahya ne Isa ne Eliasi, buli omu kwabo wa mu bakozi b’emirimu e mirungi"
  6,86,"Ne Ismail ne Iriyasa-a ne Yunus ne Luutu, buli omu ku bo twamusukkulumya ku bantu abalala"
  6,87,"Era (twalungamya abantu abalala) nga bava mu bakadde baabo ne bazzukulu baabwe ne baganda baabwe, era netubafuula ab'enjawulo, era netubalungamya ku kubo e ggolokofu"
  6,88,"Okwo kwe kulungamya kwa Katonda, alungamya na kwo oyo gwaba ayagadde mu baddube, naye singa baagatta e kintu e kirala kyonna ku Katonda, bandiyonoonekeddwa e byo bye baali bakola"
  6,89,"Abo beebo be twawa e kitabo n’obufuzi n’obwa Nabbi, kati bano bwe baba nga bawakanya e bintu e byo, mazima twabikwasa abantu abatagenda kubiwakanya"
  6,90,"Abo beebo Katonda be yalungamya, obulungamu bwabwe bwoteekwa okugoberera, ogambe nti, (kyenkola) si kibasabirako mpeera kyenkola, tekiri kyo (kintu kirala kyonna) okugyako okuba nti kujjukiza eri abantu bonna"